\'Direct thy mind to God in gratitude.’ she said, ‘who hath united us with the
first star.’

Meseemed a cloud enveloped us, shining, dense, firm and polished, like diamond
smitten by the sun.

Within itself the eternal pearl received us. as water doth receive a ray of
light, though still itself uncleft.
